{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-1","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-cat-photo-app","demoType":"onLoad","title":"Korak 1","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U ovoj radionici, nastavićete da radite sa osnovnim elementima HTML kao naslovima sekcija, pasusima i listama za izradu programa sa slikama mačke.</p>\n<p>Počnite radionicu dodavanjem elementa <code>h1</code> koji sadrži tekst <code>CatPhotoApp</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5dc174fcf86c76b9248c6eb2","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-1"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    \n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[2,4],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Reč <code>CatPhotoApp</code> mora biti u kodu. Možda želite proveriti pravopis.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /catphotoapp/i);"},{"text":"<p>Vaša komponenta <code>h1</code> treba da ima etiketu za otvaranje. Etikete za otvaranje imaju ovu sintaksu: <code>&#x3C;elementName></code>.</p>","testString":"assert.exists(document.querySelector('h1'));"},{"text":"<p>Etiketa za <code>h1</code> treba da bude u malim slovima. Prema sporazumu, sve etikete za HTML su napisane u malim slovima.</p>","testString":"assert.notMatch(code, /<\\/?H1>/);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element <code>h1</code> treba da ima zatvarajući tag. Zatvarajući tagovi imaju ovu sintaksu: <code>&#x3C;/elementName></code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /<\\/h1\\>/);"},{"text":"<p>Tekst elementa <code>h1</code> bi trebalo da bude <code>CatPhotoApp</code>. Možda ste ostavili te reči, postoje greške u pravopisu, ili se ne nalaze između otvarajućeg i zatvarajućeg taga elementa <code>h1</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(document.querySelector('h1')?.innerText?.trim().toLowerCase(), 'catphotoapp');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/#workshop-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-1","certification":"responsive-web-design-v9","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","chapter":"html","module":"basic-html","block":"workshop-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-2","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/lecture-understanding-the-html-boilerplate/what-is-utf-8-character-encoding","id":"5dc174fcf86c76b9248c6eb2","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-1"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}